verbose_text: Simultaneous dextrose infusion may contribute to increase the BCAA / aromatic amino acid ratio by reducing the endogenous aromatic amino acid load from protein catabolism, while cleaning of the bowel and/or manipulation of its microbial flora reduce endogenous ammonia production.
